           SHORT="Smartly backup partitions"

cat << EOF
Partclone is a project like the well-known backup utility "Partition Image"
a.k.a. partimage. Partclone provides utilities to backup used blocks and
designed for higher compatibility of the file system by using supported
libraries, like e2fslibs.

Supports Linux, Windows, Mac, FreeBSD, ESX file system backup/restore.
Supports btrfs, ext2/3/4, jfs, xfs, reiserfs, and reiser4 for linux file
systems.
Supports exfat, fat12/16/32, vfat and ntfs for Windows file systems.
Supports ufs for FreeBSD file system.
Support vmfs for ESX vmware server
EOF
